      "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
        {
          "@language": "en",
          "@value": "Flight enacts the same ascensional drive as the wing: an upward movement toward the pure, the divine, and the metaphysical heights, expressing the symbolic refusal of death through elevation"
