        {
          "@language": "en",
          "@value": "The behavioral tendency to collect and guard valuable objects such as gold or precious stones."
        },
        {
          "@language": "en",
          "@value": "Trolls tend to accumulate treasures because they are attracted to the materiality of things. It represents a declination of Durand's mystical structures that focus on sensory attachment."
        }
